<div class="c-reviews">
  <div class="c-reviews__header">
    <div class="c-reviews__logo">
      {% assign icon = 'icm-text-logo' %}
      {% include 'svg-icon'%}

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="c-reviews__content">
    <ul class="c-reviews__list">
      <li class="c-reviews__item">
        <div class="c-reviews__review">
          <div class="c-review">
            <div class="c-review__score">5/5</div>
            <div class="c-review__stars">
              {% assign icon = 'star' %}
              {% capture icon-star %}{% include "svg-icon" %}{% endcapture %}
              {{ icon-star }} {{ icon-star }} {{ icon-star }} {{ icon-star }} {{ icon-star }}
            </div>
            <blockquote class="c-review__quote">
              <p><strong>It’s Just Brilliant!</strong></p>
              <p>I have been using the I Clean Mini now for a while now and it’s just brilliant. I have the peace of mind that I’m not only cleaning but sanitising my home as well, without using any toxic chemicals.</p>
              <p>The mini has become part of my whole families cleaning routine, highly recommended!</p>
            </blockquote>
            <cite class="c-review__cite">Tracey Powell – Gloucestershire</cite>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
